column1: Observed Geomagnetic Storm Parameters:---- CME Note: Source region seen in AIA 193. Large filament like eruption stretching from disk center towards NE limb starting around 2014-06-25T08:45Z [-DK] CME arrival could be 2014-06-29T18:00Z or it could be the arrival of the later CME which started at the Sun around 2014-06-26T01:25Z.
